         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540"><!-- p3l5-r7 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Hd1e108">Rubrica 7</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De circumspectione prolocutionis aliene malignitatis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>¶ De circuscriptione prolocu
      <lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>tionis aliene malignitatis.
      <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>Rubrica. sexta.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e123">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/> <ref>IN leuitico c. 18</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e129"> Ait
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>deus ad      
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>moysen infras. Omnis homo ad pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>ximam sanguinis sui non accedat
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>vt reuellet turpitudinem eius. Turpitudi
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>nem patris tui et turpitudinem matris tue non
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>discooperies. Turpitudinem vxoris patris
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>tui non discooperies. Turpitudinem nurus
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>tue non reuelabis. Turpitudinem vxoris
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>fratris tui non reuelabis. Turpitudinem vxo
        <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>ris tue et filie eius non reuelabis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>¶ <ref>Salomon in prouerb. c. 26.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e156">Que viderunt
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>oculi tui ne proferas in iurgio cito ne po
        <lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>stea emendare non possis cum dehonesta
        <lb ed="#V" n="22" break="no"/>ueris amicum tuum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e167">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>¶ <ref>Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 19.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e171">Si
        <lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>cut tibi delictum noli denudare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e177">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>¶ <ref>Tullius in inuectiua in salustium.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e181">Sepe vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>di grauius offendere animos auditorum eos
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>qui aliena flagitia apte dixerunt quam eos qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>commiserunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e191">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>¶ <ref>Ouidius sine titulo siue amorum li. 2. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e195">Crede mihi nulla sunt crimina grata mari
        <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>to. Nec quemquam quamuis audiat illa inuuant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e203">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>/ <ref>Libro. 3. et fi. c. 13 et p.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e207">Non peccat que
        <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>cumque potest peccasse negare.
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>Solaque famosam culpa professa facit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>Quis furor est qua nocte latent in luce fateri:
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>Et qua clam facias facta referre palam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>¶ <ref>Auctor l. de for: honeste vite. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e223">Nisi ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>nesta causa est iustus secreta non pandit: ta
        <lb ed="#V" n="39" break="no"/>cenda enim tacet. loquenda loquitur: atque ita
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>illi alta pax est et secura tranquillitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>¶ <ref>Cato. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e237">Quod pudeat socios prudens ce
        <lb ed="#V" n="42" break="no"/>lare memento.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e244"> 
             / <ref>Capitulo. 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e246">Productus testis salua tamen ante pudorem.
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>Quantumcumque potes celare crimen amici.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e254">
               <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>¶ <ref>Gregorius in pastorali. c. 56.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e258">Plerunque <!--191.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>culpa dum absconditur effugatur: quia dum mens
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>erubescit videri quod tamen esse non metuit: eru
        <lb ed="#V" n="48" break="no"/>bescit quoniamque esse quod fugit videri.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e272">
               <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>¶ <ref>Isydorus in synonyma soliloquiorum l. 2.
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>c. 43.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e276">Operta paucis denuncia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e282">
               <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>¶ <ref>Auctor l. qui incipit astrolabi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e286">Nolo vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>rum doceas vxoris crimen amare.
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>Quod sciri potius quam fieri grauat. hunc
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>Opprobriis aurem propriis dat nemo libenter
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>Nec te nec quemquam talia scire volet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e298">
               <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>¶ <ref>Montenarius in luna cleri. c. p.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e302">Diligitur tector scelerum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>Qui conspicit audit: Et reticet: cum pace po
        <lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>test ducere vitam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-d1e312">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>¶ <ref>Prouerbia vulgaria.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62540-Qd1e316">Chi alde ve e taxe po viuere en pace.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
